{"tid":306440,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"徐淑敏大女7歲生日開party 收大提琴鋼琴相機 偷影爹地黃浩出浴照","createTime":"2017-07-02T14:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T07:24:06.000Z","uid":22349,"like":7,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8539c0f7e52efb3f96db23a2c4bfcc9edd65f297","tid":306440,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T14:00:22.000Z","msg":"經常有人話「囡囡係爸爸的前世情人」，不過其實又點止爸爸呢？媽咪都一樣！好似靚太徐淑敏同老公黃浩出名係廿四孝父母，今日係兩人的大女黃心瑤7歲生日，他們上周已提早為愛女舉行生日派對慶祝，大女更挑選了相機做禮物，不過她在家中試機時，竟然影到爸爸的「裸」照，十分爆笑！<br />\n<br />\n今日係徐淑敏（Suki）與老公黃浩（Kenny）的大女黃心瑤（Vianna）的7歲生日，早於上星期Kenny便邀請了一班金融界的俊男美女到家中作客，順道慶祝Vianna的生日。而在上周六，靚媽Suki更為囡囡打點一切，在淺水灣的Maggie &amp; Rose Family Members Club舉行生日派對，並邀請了Vianna的同學仔一齊慶生，總共招待了約100人，場面非常熱鬧！<br />\n<br />\n去年Vianna生日就在家中舉行了一個以「英式下午茶」為主題的Party，而今次Suki和Kenny則安排了愛女與其他小朋友齊齊親自落手學整Pizza，Kenny透露：「佢哋整咗1個鐘Pizza，Vianna玩到好開心，仲唔捨得走！我同Suki走咗之後，佢繼續留低玩咗3個鐘。」<br />\n<br />\n今次真係樂而忘返！問到送了甚麼禮物給囡囡？Kenny指買了一個大鋼琴和小鋼琴給Vianna，好讓她學習彈鋼琴，另外還帶同三個愛女到玩具店自選禮物，每人3份，因為大女生日可再選多一份，總共10份，皆大歡喜！Kenny更自爆在家中發生一件小趣事，他說：「Vianna揀咗一部卡通相機，佢影相好叻，有次影到我沖完涼冇着衫嘅相，我即刻話唔可以咁樣影媽咪，點知Vianna話媽咪先唔會咁樣走出嚟，哈哈！」"},{"pid":"7ca72933fa8a4182fe1af83017f1c95bd8c13303","tid":306440,"uid":22349,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T14:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/220059_af93470b43c37e709f72f4a2425240f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F220059_af93470b43c37e709f72f4a2425240f1.jpg&h=88ad877a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/220113_55c1c61471a9c3dba3389f6231cda32c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F220113_55c1c61471a9c3dba3389f6231cda32c.jpg&h=f3010657&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/220135_af4509c30ad408f57fa2da3861755b26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F220135_af4509c30ad408f57fa2da3861755b26.jpg&h=1d3fbf49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大女Vianna 今日踏入7歲，已經長得亭亭玉立。"},{"pid":"a4ba8ba0900c903ef834b024a45058f72b93035e","tid":306440,"uid":115776,"like":195,"dislike":2,"score":193,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"全部同佢老豆一撚樣"},{"pid":"5c8758c2de89dfdfc04c350227141db4dcc2a137","tid":306440,"uid":34189,"like":118,"dislike":1,"score":117,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T14:55:36.000Z","msg":"慘,一D老母靚基因都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad441a638028ec4d46653acb4df2ca840f697bd","tid":306440,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T14:56:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e765a1ba8b1f5c7e7eee694bd2e49dbf00afef6","tid":306440,"uid":29929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:17:52.000Z","msg":"睇定d 有潛力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b49c38e13c50190628a7e79b1efdbad69a666f","tid":306440,"uid":60301,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T20:15:20.000Z","msg":"其實都幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c269ec3ddbec7bdb14e3ceadcb38fe0f388608b7","tid":306440,"uid":91736,"like":8,"dislike":24,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T21:23:22.000Z","msg":"關我撚事 乜鳩都擺上黎"},{"pid":"1d8b28a0373a6346a91df092ff1c2c195ae0dfb0","tid":306440,"uid":49247,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T22:23:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慘,一D老母靚基因都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能有奶呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f377984768c9d358810a1a61ff7069793942e7","tid":306440,"uid":6273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T22:38:36.000Z","msg":"Suki真係好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6faea84f93279